%20product%20quality%20and%20friendly%20service%26quot%3B%20for%20See's%20generating%20%24857%20million%20in%20pre-tax%20income%20since%20Berkshire%20took%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESee's%20pre-tax%20profit%20in%20millions%20was%20about%2010%25%20of%20Huggins'%20age%20when%20he%20took%20over%20aged%2046%2C%20Buffett%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%20That%20ratio%20soared%20to%20100%25%20by%20the%20time%20he%20turned%2074%2C%20the%20investor%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20discovered%20this%20mathematical%20relationship%20%E2%80%94%20let's%20call%20it%20Huggins'%20Law%20%E2%80%94%20Charlie%20and%20I%20now%20become%20giddy%20at%20the%20mere%20thought%20of%20Chuck's%20birthday%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Buying%20a%20furniture%20store%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20received%20a%20particularly%20nice%20birthday%20gift%20in%201983%20when%20Mrs%20B%2C%20the%2089-year-old%20owner%20of%20Nebraska%20Furniture%20Mart%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-89-mrs-b-fortune-500-ceo-2019-12-1028763487%23%5C%22%3Eagreed%20to%20sell%20the%20company%20to%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20back%20to%20August%2030%2C%201983%20%E2%80%94%20my%20birthday%20%E2%80%94%20when%20I%20went%20to%20see%20Mrs%20B%20(Rose%20Blumkin)%2C%20carrying%20a%20one%20and%20a%20quarter-page%20purchase%20proposal%20for%20NFM%20that%20I%20had%20drafted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.berkshirehathaway.com%2Fletters%2F2013ltr.pdf%5C%22%3E2013%20shareholder%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMrs%20B%20accepted%20my%20offer%20without%20changing%20a%20word%2C%20and%20we%20completed%20the%20deal%20without%20the%20involvement%20of%20investment%20bankers%20or%20lawyers%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20the%20company's%20financial%20statements%20were%20unaudited%2C%20I%20had%20no%20worries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BMrs%20B%20simply%20told%20me%20what%20was%20what%2C%20and%20her%20word%20was%20good%20enough%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Business%20at%20a%20party%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20shared%20an%20example%20of%20Berkshire's%20%26quot%3Bcarefully%20crafted%20and%20sophisticated%20acquisition%20strategy%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.berkshirehathaway.com%2Fletters%2F1996.html%5C%22%3E1996%20shareholder%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investor%20tried%20to%20get%20out%20of%20attending%20the%2040th%20birthday%20party%20of%20his%20nephew's%20wife%2C%20Jane%20Rogers%2C%20but%20agreed%20to%20go%20after%20learning%20he%20would%20be%20sitting%20next%20to%20Jane's%20dad%2C%20Roy%20Dinsdale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20party%2C%20Dinsdale%20revealed%20he%20had%20attended%20a%20directors'%20meeting%20at%20Kansas%20Bankers%20Surety%2C%20an%20insurance%20firm%20that%20Buffett%20had%20long%20admired.%20Buffett%20told%20Dinsdale%20to%20let%20him%20know%20if%20the%20company%20ever%20came%20up%20for%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20Dinsdale%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20later%20that%20contained%20KBS's%20financial%20information.%20He%20called%20Dinsdale%20the%20next%20day%20to%20offer%20%2475%20million%20for%20the%20company%2C%20and%20the%20pair%20soon%20struck%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20now%20scheming%20to%20get%20invited%20to%20Jane's%20next%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20anyone%20owns%20a%20company%20that%20meets%20Berkshire's%20requirements%20%26quot%3Band%20if%20I%20fail%20to%20make%20the%20next%20birthday%20party%20you%20attend%20...%20give%20me%20a%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E6.%20'I'm%20really%20good%20at%20this'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20famously%20hires%20and%20trusts%20top-notch%20managers%20to%20run%20Berkshire's%20various%20businesses%2C%20freeing%20him%20to%20focus%20on%20allocating%20c