r%20caste%20majority%20position%20in%20India.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20RSS%2C%20the%20supremacist%20organisation%20of%20the%20minority%20upper%20castes%20(less%20than%2010%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20India)%2C%20and%20its%20(conveniently%20disavowable)%20offshoots%20are%20at%20liberty%20to%20violate%20all%20constitutional%20and%20international%20norms%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fcrime%2Fnuh-haryana-bajrang-dal-communal-violence-arrest-muslim-youth%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20take%20out%20armed%20processions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-mosques-arson-internet-remains-suspended%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eattack%20mosques%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fchristians-attacked-in-delhi-church-during-sunday-service%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echurches%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We%20should%20consider%20the%20differences%20in%20the%20political%20lines%20of%20demarcation%20between%20the%20associations%20and%20the%20assemblies%20of%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20and%20of%20the%20upper%20caste%20minority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20recent%20hate%20campaign%20of%20the%20RSS%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emafia%20famiglia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20began%20in%20the%20Nuh%20district%20of%20Haryana%20in%20July%202023%20against%20Muslims.%20If%20we%20perceive%20it%20and%20speak%20of%20it%20the%20way%20they%20want%20us%20to%20%E2%80%93%20in%20terms%20like%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20majority%E2%80%9D%20versus%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20minority%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20we%20will%20be%20morally%20responsible%20for%20the%20crimes%20against%20humanity%20which%20await%20us%20in%20a%20future%20of%20India.%20Most%20conflicts%20in%20India%2C%20political%20and%20of%20other%20kinds%2C%20including%20the%20events%20in%20Nuh%20are%20concerned%20with%20prol