%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Brahminical%20minority%20position%2C%20as%20asserted%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fviolence-in-maharashtra-as-dalits-protest-death-of-28-year-old-in-bhima-koregaon-clashes%2Fstory-zerVWqrSjLjF2x53oHMVXL.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhil%20Bharatiya%20Brahmin%20Mahasangh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20so%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%2C%20not%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%2C%20negative%20freedom%20of%20association%20may%20appear%20as%20it%20did%20in%20Nazi%20Germany%2C%20everyone%20may%20be%20made%20an%20automatic%20member%20of%20the%20RSS.%20Before%20that%20comes%20about%2C%20we%20should%20breathe%20life%20back%20into%20the%20constitution%20through%20the%20exercise%20of%20the%20rights%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20fitness%20test%20of%20the%20constitution%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20health%20of%20the%20constitution%20must%20be%20tested%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20in%20the%20halls%20of%20justice%2C%20and%20these%20tests%20are%20the%20responsibility%20of%20everyone%2C%20not%20just%20the%20activists%20and%20lawyers.%20We%20should%20gather%20over%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20under%20an%20idea%20whenever%20possible.%20We%20should%20form%20newer%20associations%20in%20the%20mode%20of%20weekend%20clubs%20to%20educate%20one%20another%20about%20the%20political%20history%20of%20India%2C%20mourn%20its%20present%2C%20and%20draft%20its%20future.%20We%20should%20associate%20and%20share%20books%2C%20articles%20and%20other%20resources%20so%20that%20we%20become%20the%20egalitarian%20gathering%20of%20an%20effervescent%20power%20opposing%20an%20evanescent%20force%20composed%20of%20barely%20literate%20goons%20and%20clowns.%20We%20should%20also%20visit%20those%20neighbourhoods%20within%20our%20neighbourhoods%20that%20are%20kept%20apart%20under%20caste%20and%20religious%20apartheid.%20Above%20all%2C%20associate%20in%20the%20greatest%20of%20numbers%20for%20egalitarianism%20as%20such.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20acts%20will%20be%20policed%2C%20mobbed%2C%20and%20terrorised%20with%20the%20connivance%20of%20some%20office%20bearers%20of%20the%20institutions%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20by%20the%20cowards%20who%20walk%20the%20streets%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20terrify%20everyone%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Freligion%2Fhow-upper-castes-invented-hindu-majority%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20recently%20invented%20religion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20RSS%2C%20as%20we%20have%20known%20them%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20anti-colonial%20movement%20and%20since%201947%2C%20are%20cowards%20who%20operate%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20in%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20crowds%20or%2C%20today%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fformer-delhi-police-officer-who-let-kapil-mishra-make-fiery-speech-before-delhi-riots-seeks-medal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20security%20offered%20by%20high%20ranking%20policemen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20we%20should%20freely%20assemble%20in%20the%20open%20in%20order%20to%20open%20politics%20again%20as%20the%20quest%20for%20freedom%3B%20bearing%20moral%20courage%20and%20the%20creative%20power%20of%20lamentation%20within%3B%20and%20must%20return%20again%20and%20again%20in%20greater%20numbers%20festively%20and%20peacefully%20so%20that%20we%20become%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekinesis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20freedom%20ourselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062v