uot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBurger%20King%20must%20face%20a%20lawsuit%20claiming%20its%20Whoppers%20look%20much%20larger%20and%20meatier%20on%20its%20menus%20after%20a%20judge%20turned%20down%20the%20company's%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20class-action%20lawsuit%2C%20first%20filed%20in%20March%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburger-king-named-in-false-advertising-lawsuit-over-whopper-size-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccuses%20the%20burger%20giant%20of%20misleading%20customers%20about%20its%20menu%20items%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20social-media%20reviews%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-burgers-at-burger-king-ranked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsider%20article%20from%202020%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBurger%20King%20advertises%20its%20burgers%20as%20large%20burgers%20compared%20to%20competitors%20and%20containing%20oversized%20meat%20patties%20and%20ingredients%20that%20overflow%20over%20the%20bun%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20Burger%20King%20changed%20the%20photos%20of%20Whoppers%20used%20in%20promotional%20materials%20to%20make%20the%20overall%20burger%20look%20around%20a%20third%20bigger%20and%20the%20beef%20content%20more%20than%20twice%20as%20large.%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Whopper%20and%20the%20beef%20patty%20increased%20materially%20in%20Burger%20King's%20advertisements%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20beef%20or%20ingredients%20contained%20in%20the%20actual%20Whopper%20that%20customers%20receive%20did%20not%20increase%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20amended%20in%20May%202022%2C%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20alleges%20that%20Burger%20King%20%26quot%3Bmaterially%20overstates%20the%20size%20of%20nearly%20every%20menu%20item%20in%20its%20current%20advertisements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBurger%20King's%20actions%20are%20especially%20concerning%20now%20that%20inflation%2C%20food%2C%20and%20meat%20prices%20are%20very%20high%20and%20many%20consumers%2C%20especially%20lower%20income%20consumers%2C%20are%20struggling%20financially%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20in%20May%202022%2C%20Burger%20King%20said%20that%20that%20each%20sandwich%20it%20sold%20looked%20different%20because%20they're%20handmade%20and%20that%20the%20photos%20on%20its%20menu%20%26quot%3Baccurately%26quot%3B%20showed%20the%20ingredients.%20It%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Breasonable%26quot%3B%20customers%20wouldn't%20expect%20each%20burger%20to%20come%20out%20looking%20exactly%20like%20it%20does%20in%20adverts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20motion%20also%20says%20that%20the%20customers%20shouldn't%20have%20%26quot%3Bexpected%26quot%3B%20the%20burgers%20to%20contain%20more%20beef%20than%20they%20did%20because%20it%20states%20portion%20sizes%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bk.com%2Fmenu%2Fpicker-b1d74685-2756-47f7-a6a2-5e28441a868c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Whopper%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20listed%20as%20containing%20a%20quarter-pounder%20patty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFood%20in%20advertisements%20is%20and%20always%20has%20been%20styled%20to%20make%20it%20look%20as%20appetizing%20as%20possible.%20That%20is%20hardly%20news%3B%20reasonable%20consumers%20viewing%20food%20advertising%20know%20it%20innately.%20This%20lawsuit%20unreasonably%20pretends%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20Burger%20King%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%20on%20August%2023%2C%202023%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20Roy%20Altman%20granted%20Burger%20King's%20requests%20to%20dismiss%20claims%20related%20to%20its%20online%20and%20TV%20ads%20as%20well%20as%20claims%20that%20the%20company%20violated%20state%20consumer-protection%20laws.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20plaintiffs%20could%20still%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20lawsuit%3A%20claims%20of%20breach%20of%20contract%2C%20negligent%20misrepresentation%2C%20and%20unjust%20enrichment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20are%20we%20to%20decide%20whether%20such%20a%20seemingly%20substantial%20difference%20between%20what%20was%20promised%20and%20what%20was%20sold%20was%20(or%20was%20not)%20enough%20to%20alter%20the%20purchasing%20preferences%20of%20reasonable%20American%20consumers%3F%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote%20in%20the%20filing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFar%20better%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20us%2C%20to%20leave%20that%20determination%20to%20the%20consumers%20themselves%2C%20who%20%E2%80%94%20if%20the%20case%20survives%20that%20far%20%E2%80%94%20will%20get%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20jury%20box%20and%20tell%20us%20what%20reasonable%20people%20think%20on%20the%20subject.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20judge's%20ruling%2C%20a%20Burger%20King%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20plaintiffs'%20claims%20are%20false.%20The%20flame-grilled%20beef%20patties%20portrayed%20in%20our%20advertising%20are%20the%20same%20patties%20used%20in%20the%20millions%20of%20Whopper%20sandwiches%20we%20serve%20to%20Guests%20nationwide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20lawyers%20representing%20the%20plaintiffs%2C%20New%20York-based%20James%20C.%20Kelly%2C%20has%20also%20filed%20similar%20class-action%20cases%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fman-sued-taco-bell-too-little-beef-mexican-pizza-crunchwrap-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaco%20Bell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjckellylaw.com%2Fwendys-false-ads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWendy's%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjckellylaw.com%2Fmcdonalds-false-ads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburger-king-lawsuit-whoppers-look-bigger-meatier-menus-dismiss-food-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693391581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef121c26dda200194d98b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburger-king-lawsuit-whoppers-look-bigger-meatier-menus-dismiss-food-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Burger%20King%2C%20whose%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20was%20partly%20granted%2C%20said%20the%20claims%20made%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20were%C2%A0%26quot%3Bfalse.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburger-king-lawsuit-whoppers-look-bigger-meatier-menus-dismiss-food-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vivek%E2%80%99s%20meme%20trolling%20SRK's%20Jawan%20goes%20viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693391511000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103210628%2Cimgsize-33494.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvivek-agnihotris-meme-trolling-shah-rukh-khans-jawan-and-prabhas-salaar-goes-viral%2Farticleshow%2F103210600.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103210600.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFilmmaker%20Vivek%20Agnihotri%20recently%20shared%20a%20meme%20on%20social%20media%20comparing%20the%20audience's%20anticipation%20for%20different%20movies%2C%20including%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20'Jawan'%20and%20Prabhas'%20'Salaar'.%20The%20post%20went%20viral%2C%20sparking%20comments%20from%20internet%20users.%20Despite%20the%20meme%20controversy%2C%20Vivek%20expressed%20support%20for%20'Jawan'%20and%20mentioned%20his%20upcoming%20film%20'The%20Vaccine%20War'.%20The%20movie%2C