3D%5C%22Andrew%20Slimmon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef067496b7920019ca378c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrew%20Slimmon%20is%20a%20senior%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20%24665%20billion%20investment%20management%20business%3Cp%3ECNBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDespite%20a%20downbeat%20August%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20is%20still%20boasting%20impressive%20year-to-date%20gains.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20benchmark%20stock-market%20gauge%20is%20up%20over%2017%25%20so%20far%20in%202023%2C%20and%20one%20expert%20sees%20it%20climbing%20even%20higher.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMorgan%20Stanley's%20Andrew%20Slimmon%20sees%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20nearing%205%2C000%20by%20year-end%20%E2%80%93%20what%20would%20be%20an%2011%25%20rise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20stock%20market%20has%20enjoyed%20a%20strong%20rally%20in%202023%2C%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20mega-cap%20tech%20stocks%20boosting%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20by%20more%20than%2017%25%20year-to-date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20expert%20believes%20the%20run%20could%20continue%20even%20further%20%E2%80%93%20predicting%20the%20index%20could%20reach%20%26quot%3Bcloser%26quot%3B%20to%205%2C000%20points%20by%20the%20end%20of%202023%20%E2%80%93%20in%20what%20would%20mark%20an%2011%25%20increase%20from%20Tuesday's%20close%20of%204497.%20That%20could%20also%20mean%20the%20index%20topping%20the%20current%20record%20high%20of%20about%204%2C818%2C%20reached%20in%20January%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20get%20closer%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20the%20pain%20of%20being%20underweight%20equities%2C%20and%20the%20resultant%20lack%20of%20performance%20is%20going%20to%20intensify%20forcing%20positive%20fund%20flows%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Slimmon%2C%20managing%20director%20and%20senior%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%20Investment%20Management%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F08%2F30%2Fmorgan-stanleys-slimmon-says-markets-will-rally-names-3-stocks.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC's%20%26quot%3BStreet%20Signs%20Asia%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20weak%20run%20in%20August%20has%20seen%20stocks%20pull%20back%20slightly%20from%20their%20stunning%20first%20half%20%E2%80%93%20but%20Slimmon%20sees%20strong%20third-quarter%20earnings%20helping%20the%20market%20resume%20its%20advance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYear-over-year%20quarterly%20earnings%20are%20going%20to%20inflect%20from%20negative%20to%20positive%20after%20Q3.%20Historically%2C%20this%20is%20greeted%20positively%20by%20equities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portfolio%20manager%20added%20that%20he%20sees%20investors%20flocking%20to%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BMagnificent%20Seven%26quot%3B%20group%20of%20shares%20over%20the%20next%20quarter%20as%20the%20summer%20lull%20draws%20to%20a%20close.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20Meta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Nvidia%20and%20Tesla%20comprise%20the%20set%20of%20seven%20mega-cap%20tech%20stocks%20that%20have%20propelled%20the%20stock%20market%20upward%20this%20year%2C%20thanks%20to%20investor%20excitement%20surrounding%20artificial%20intelligence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20already-high%20valuations%2C%20Slimmon%20sees%20further%20room%20to%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20much%20as%20these%20companies%20have%20had%20a%20very%20good%20year%20to%20date%2C%20they're%20still%20below%20where%20they%20ended%202021%20%E2%80%93%20Nvidia's%20the%20exception.%20These%20companies%20are%20lower%20today%20than%20where%20they%20ended%202021%20because%20last%20year%20was%20worse%20than%20the%20rally%20year%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20in%20particular%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20