ased%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Rika%20Tajima%2C%20a%2034-year-old%20woman%20from%20Japan%2C%20about%20her%20journey%20to%20travel%20to%20London%2C%20where%20she%20froze%20her%20eggs.%20This%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20a%20relative%20call%20me%20worthless%2C%20even%20though%20I%20have%20tried%20really%20hard%20with%20my%20academics%20or%20work%20%E2%80%94%20all%20because%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20child.%20And%20that%20really%20bothered%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%2034%20now%20and%20have%20spent%20the%20bulk%20of%20my%20life%20really%20focused%20on%20studying%20and%20my%20career%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20balance%20my%20work%20and%20personal%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20gynecologist%2C%20who%20is%20the%20same%20age%20as%20me%2C%20told%20me%20it%20was%20a%20good%20time%20to%20consider%20egg%20freezing%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20go.%20But%20I%20felt%20guilty%20because%20I%20was%20going%20to%20be%20spending%20money%20and%20time%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20had%20to%20spend%20if%20I%20just%20had%20a%20child%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20more%20choices%20for%20myself%20in%20the%20future%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I'll%20have%20a%20child%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20myself%20that%20leeway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20up%20multiple%20egg-freezing%20hospitals%20in%20Japan%20and%20some%20of%20them%20also%20worked%20for%20single%20women%2C%20not%20just%20couples.%20I%20went%20to%20one%2C%20but%20it%20felt%20like%20were%20treating%20me%20like%20a%20customer%20rather%20than%20a%20patient%2C%20something%20that%20made%20me%20feel%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20late%20last%20year%2C%20I%20attended%20the%20SkyDeck%20accelerator%20program%20for%20startup%20founders%20in%20Berkeley.%20It%20was%20there%20I%20met%20Abhi%20Ghavalkar%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20a%20startup%20called%20Milvia%2C%20which%20aimed%20to%20dramatically%20improve%20the%20egg-freezing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilvia%20calls%20itself%20the%20Airbnb%20of%20fertility%20tourism.%20It%20books%20trips%2C%20including%20flights%20and%20accommodation%2C%20for%20patients%20who%20want%20to%20undergo%20egg%20freezing%20and%20IVF%20abroad.%20It%20has%20partnerships%20with%20clinics%20in%20London%20so%20patients%20don't%20have%20the%20hassle%20of%20finding%20a%20doctor%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20egg%20freezing%20in%20the%20US%20can%20cost%20%2411%2C000%20for%20an%20initial%20treatment%2C%20excluding%20medication%20and%20monthly%20storage%20costs%3B%20the%20total%20process%2C%20including%20storage%20costs%2C%20usually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fertilityiq.com%2Fegg-freezing%2Fthe-costs-of-egg-freezing%23breaking-down-the-likely-costs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehits%20%2430%2C000%20to%20%2440%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20UK%2C%20treatment%20costs%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.refinery29.com%2Fen-gb%2F2020%2F11%2F10167327%2Fegg-freezing-uk-cost%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%244000%20on%20average%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20excluding%20monthly%20storage%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20but%20can%20stretch%20up%20to%20%2410%2C000%20if%20including%20storage%2C%20medication%2C%20and%20thawing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20then%20I%20thought%3A%20%26quot%3BWhy%20not%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20could%20make%20this%20into%20a%20positive%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20and%20get%20that%20negative%20connotation%20about%20egg%20freezing%20out%20of%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaking%20a%20vacation%20out%20of%20my%20journey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELondon%20appealed%20to%20me%20from%20a%20tourism%20point%20of%20view%20but%20also%20because%20egg-freezing%20options%20are%20more%20researched%20and%20well-established%20than%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20coming%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20I%20had%20consultations%20with%20Milvia%2C%20and%20paid%20them%20to%20book%20my%20Airbnb%2C%20flights%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20concierge%20service.%20I%20chose%20one%20on%20the%20cheaper%20end%2C%20in%20West%20London%2C%20near%20a%20school.%20I%20actually%20had%20a%20fridge%20in%20my%20room%20as%20well%2C%20which%20was%20really%20helpful%20because%20I%20needed%20to%20store%20some%20of%20my%20medication%20there.%20Milvia%20has%20partnered%20with%20clinics%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20so%20that%20took%20the%20hassle%20out%20of%20the%20process%20of%20researching%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20had%20some%20medications%20prescribed%20to%20me%2C%20and%20I%20took%20those%20twice%20daily%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20evening.%20On%20my%20second%20day%20in%20London%2C%20I%20had%20my%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20baseline%20scan.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20I%20started%20self-injecting%20in%20the%20stomach.%20Five%20days%20later%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20second%20scan.%20They%20said%20that%20I%20could%20start%20my%20additional%20medication.%20Now%20I%20was%20self-injecting%20in%20my%20stomach%20once%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20once%20in%20the%20evening.%20I%20also%20went%20to%20the%20hospital%20the%20following%20weekend%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20how%20I%20was%20feeling%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20I%20used%20to%20talk%20to%20Akash%20Ghavalkar%2C%20the%20COO%20of%20Milvia%2C%20about%20how%20I'd%20like%20to%20spend%20my%20day.%20Sometimes%20I%20would%20go%20to%20a%20coworking%20space%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20work%2C%20but%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20sightsee.%20Milvia%20would%20set%20up%20the%20visits%20and%20help%20me%20with%20booking%20train%20tickets%20and%20tour%20guides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20about%20half%20my%20time%20working%20and%20half%20my%20time%20as%20a%20tourist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rika%20at%20her%20graffiti%20workshop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e876a852bc2d001991e534%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERika%20at%20her%20graffiti%20workshop.%3Cp%3ERika%20Tajima.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMilvia%20also%20booked%20my%20plane%2C%20which%20was%20a%20direct%20flight%2C%20but%20the%20ticket%20was%20flexible%20because%20I%20may%20have%20needed%20to%20stay%20longer%20if%20my%20eggs%20weren't%20ready%20for%20retrieval%20by%20the%20scheduled%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20felt%20anxious%20before%20retrieving%20my%20eggs%20%E2%80%94%20but%20having%20support%20around%20me%20helped%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Japan%2C%20couples%20that%20are%20struggling%20to%20conceive%20can%20get%20public%20health%20insurance%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-03-31%2Fjapan-subsidizes-costly-ivf-treatments-to-lift-falling-birthrate%3FleadSource%3Dreddit_wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20subsidize%20up%20to%2070%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20their%20fertility%20treatments%20such%20as%20IVF.%20However%2C%20if%20you're%20single%2C%20there%20aren't%20as%20many%20coverage%20options%20for%20egg-freezing%20costs%20across%20the%20whole%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nurse%20in%20the%20UK%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20inject%20myself%20with%20medication%2C%20and%20showed%20me%20some%20videos.%20I%20was%20fiddling%20around%20and%20it%20took%20me%20around%2030%20minutes%20on%20the%20first%20try.%20It%20was%20still%20a%20bit%20scary%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20egg%20retrieval%20process%20went%20as%20scheduled.%20I%20took%20all%20my%20medication.%20The%20Milvia%20staff%20were%20there%20as%20I%20was%20the%20first%20patient%20on%20their%20program%2C%20so%20that%20helped%20my%20anxiety%2C%20which%20I%20think%20was%20caused%20by%20my%20hormones.%20All%20of%20a%20sudden%20I%20was%20scared%20about%20whether%20it%20would%20work%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20took%20under%20an%20hour%20overall%2C%20and%20then%20I%20went%20back%20to%20my%20accommodation%20to%20sleep.%20I%20flew%20back%20to%20Japan%20on%20the%20Saturday%2C%20and%20in%20the%20days%20between%20that%2C%20I%20was%20taking%20walks%20and%20relaxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20came%20back%20to%20Japan%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20people%20think%20of%20me%20as%20someone%20who%20is%20more%20serious%20about%20their%20life%20decisions.%20My%20friends%20asked%20me%20how%20it%20was%20and%20they're%20considering%20egg%20freezing%20more%20seriously.%20My%20parents%20were%20happy%20to%20hear%20that%20it%20went%20well.%20My%2089-year-old%20grandpa%20liked%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20traveled%20to%20London%2C%20it%20made%20it%20more%20of%20a%20celebratory%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20sometimes%2C%20it%20felt%20a%20bit%20lonely.%20I'm%20interested%20in%20the%20community%20aspect%20that%20Milvia%20can%20provide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20had%20my%20first%20self-injection%20in%20London%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20nice%20to%20have%20a%20nurse%20with%20me.%20Speaking%20to%20friends%20during%20my%20mood%20swings%20would%20have%20been%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20more%20expensive%20than%20it%20would%20have%20been%20if%20I%20had%20frozen%20my%20eggs%20in%20Japan.%20But%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20natural%20disasters%20in%20Japan%2C%20and%20I%20also%20travel%20a%20lot%20for%20work.%20So%20I%20thought%20storing%20the%20eggs%20overseas%20would%20be%20a%20nice%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20procedures%20and%20medicine%20cost%20around%20%246000%2C%20the%20accommodation%20and%20Milvia%20service%20fee%20was%20%243000%2C%20and%20flights%20were%20%242000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20expenses%20for%20the%20holiday%20were%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20reach%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20worth%20it%20because%20it%20made%20for%20a%20positive%20and%20memorable%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20interested%20in%20sharing%20your%20experience%20with%20fertility%20technology%2C%20or%20traveling%