0we%20think%20can%20help%20us.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20response%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohebi%2C%20who%20met%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20a%20central%20Delhi%20lane%20outside%20the%20headquarters%20of%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%E2%80%99%20cultural%20wing%2C%20Indian%20Council%20for%20Cultural%20Relations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%2C%20along%20with%20a%20group%20of%2020%20to%2030%20other%20students%2C%20had%20come%20to%20ICCR%20to%20meet%20with%20officials%20to%20persuade%20them%20to%20understand%20their%20situation.%20She%20was%20not%20too%20hopeful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20no%20response.%20It%20is%20not%20safe%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Kabul.%20You%20know%20how%20it%20is%20for%20girls%20out%20there.%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20allowed%20to%20do%20anything.%20It%20is%20not%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20tugging%20at%20her%20white%20scarf.%20With%20her%20visa%20set%20to%20expire%20next%20month%2C%20time%20is%20running%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2022%2F08%2F1124662%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UN%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Afghanistan%20is%20the%20only%20country%20in%20the%20world%20where%20girls%20are%20banned%20from%20going%20to%20high%20school%20and%20effectively%20barred%20from%20political%20participation.%20Afghan%20women%20are%20now%20mostly%20restricted%20from%20working%20outside%20the%20home%2C%20they%20must%20cover%20their%20faces%20in%20public%2C%20and%20they%20have%20to%20be%20accompanied%20by%20a%20male%20chaperone%20when%20they%20travel%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20week%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66636750%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earound%20100%20Afghan%20women%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20who%20had%20secured%20education%20scholarships%20in%20UAE%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20leave%20when%20they%20arrived%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParwana%20Hussaini%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20who%20completed%20her%20masters%20in%20sociology%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20is%20also%20at%20her%20wit%E2%80%99s%20end.%20%E2%80%9CI%20know%20from%20my%20friends%20who%20had%20finished%20and%20gone%20back%20earlier%20before%20the%20Taliban%20came%20back%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20very%20difficult%E2%80%A6they%20can%E2%80%99t%20leave%20the%20house%20at%20all.%20They%20are%20all%20trapped.%20I%20know%20that%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20go%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20phone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20her%20visa%20running%20out%20in%20December%2C%20she%20still%20has%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20time%20to%20remain%20in%20India.%20But%20such%20a%20temporal%20buffer%20is%20not%20a%20cause%20for%20celebration%20to%20her.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20my%20teachers%20suggested%20that%20I%20apply%20for%20a%20course.%20I%20know%20that%20I%20may%20not%20get%20in%20as%20it%20is%20already%20too%20late%2C%20but%20that%20may%20help%20me%20to%20stay%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20helplessly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20used%20the%20scholarships%20as%20a%20way%20to%20leverage%20influence%20in%20the%20years%20of%20the%20Afghan%20Republic.%20It%20used%20to%20give%20500%20scholarships%20per%20year%2C%20which%20increased%20to%201%2C000%20from%202012-2013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FMy-Enemys-Enemy-Afghanistan-Withdrawal%2Fdp%2F0190685824%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%202017%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20Avinash%20Paliwal%20described%20the%20higher%20education%20scholarships%20offered%20by%20New%20Delhi%20as%20a%20diplomatic%20tool%20%E2%80%9Cco-opt%20provincial%20Afghan%20politicians%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELess%20than%20a%20year%20before%20the%20Taliban%20rolled%20into%20Kabul%2C%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20had%20boasted%20about%20the%20Indian%20education%20scholarships%20for%20Afghans.%20%E2%80%9CMore%20than%2065%2C000%20Afghan%20students%20have%20studied%20in%20India%20under%20various%20scholarship%20programmes%20and%20while%20I%20speak%2015%2C000%20students%20are%20presently%20%5Bat%20present%5D%20studying%20in%20India.%20Three%20thousand%20scholarships%20so%20far%20have%20been%20granted%20to%20young%20Afghan%20women%20to%20pursue%20higher%20studies%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FSpeeches-Statements.htm%3Fdtl%2F33235%2Feams%2Bremarks%2Bat%2Bafghanistan%2B2020%2Bconference%2Bon%2B24%2Bnovember%2B2020%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20told%20a%20donors%20conference%20in%20November%202020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcourse-conducted-by-mea-for-taliban-staff-in-kabul-angers-afghan-students-report%5C%22%3ECourse%20Conducted%20by%20MEA%20for%20Taliban%20Staff%20in%20Kabul%20Angers%20Afghan%20Students%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20those%20who%20got%20these%20scholarships%20are%20now%20left%20stumped%20by%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20have%20spent%20the%20last%20few%20months%20on%20repetitive%20rounds%20of%20visits%20to%20local%20ICCR%20offices%2C%20lawmakers%2C%20the%20Afghan%20embassy%20and%20the%20MEA.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20particularly%2C%20students%20say%20they%20have%20had%20multiple%20meetings%20with%20ICCR%20officials.%20But%20that%20has%20shed%20little%20clarity%20on%20their%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20tell%20us%20that%20n