t%20is%20critical%20that%20you%20do%20not%20make%20such%20payments%20in%20a%20haste.%20According%20to%20senior%20cyber%20police%20officers%2C%20vehicle%20owners%20must%20check%20such%20messages%20carefully%20before%20clicking%20on%20any%20link.%20A%20key%20way%20to%20identify%20real%20messages%20is%20that%20they%20will%20have%20details%20of%20your%20vehicle%2C%20its%20engine%20number%20and%20chassis%20number.%20Such%20information%20will%20not%20be%20on%20SMS%20traps%20sent%20by%20scammers.%20Another%20precaution%20could%20be%20to%20visit%20the%20official%20government%20website%20to%20check%20if%20you%20have%20actually%20been%20fined.%20Also%2C%20an%20e-challan%20alert%20will%20never%20come%20from%20a%20cellphone%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20To%20Do%20If%20You%20Are%20Conned%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20scammers%20are%20successful%20in%20conning%20you%2C%20lose%20no%20time%20in%20informing%20the%20authorities.%20An%20immediate%20call%20to%201930%20-%20National%20Cyber%20Crime%20Reporting%20Portal%20-%20and%20a%20timely%20complaint%20with%20www.cybercrime.gov.in%20can%20also%20help%20stop%20the%20transaction%20and%20save%20your%20hard-earned%20money.%20You%20must%20also%20contact%20your%20bank%20and%20alert%20them.%20The%20next%20step%20is%20to%20approach%20the%20nearest%20police%20station%20and%20register%20a%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%88-%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%98%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%9D%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%81%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%81!''%F0%9F%9A%A6%F0%9F%9A%97%F0%9F%9B%B5%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4