0use%20four%20without%20asking%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Complaining%20about%20things%20the%20host%20cannot%20control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20complaining%20might%20be%20necessary%20if%20a%20property%20has%20underdelivered%2C%20hosts%20get%20annoyed%20by%20trivial%20complaints%20that%20impact%20their%20reviews%20and%20booking%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolly%20Arrowsmith%20has%20been%20an%20Airbnb%20%26quot%3Bsuperhost%26quot%3B%20for%20four%20years%2C%20renting%20out%20her%20apartment%20in%20Islington%2C%20London.%20She's%20still%20received%20a%20fair%20share%20of%20complaints%20she%20felt%20were%20beyond%20her%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArrowsmith%20told%20Insider%20guests%20once%20complained%20%26quot%3Bthey%20didn't%20like%20that%20there%20was%20a%20basement%20flat%20below%20their%20ground-floor%20flat%2C%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20London%20apartment.%20%26quot%3BOr%20criticizing%20the%20external%20paintwork%20and%20basing%20their%20review%20on%20that%20when%20the%20flat%20was%20immaculate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20silly%20complaints.%20I%20can't%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20way%20the%20property%20was%20built%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Stealing%20items%20from%20the%20Airbnb%20property%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EArrowsmith%20remembered%20how%20disappointed%20she%20was%20after%20a%20Moomin%20mug%2C%20worth%20about%20%2430%2C%20went%20missing%20after%20a%20guest's%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20taken%20other%20things%20like%20towels%2C%20umbrellas%2C%20full-sized%20shampoo%2C%20shampoo%2C%20conditioner%2C%20and%20hand-wash%20bottles%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20She%20told%20Insider%20she%20was%20shocked%20people%20think%20it's%20acceptable%20to%20steal%20items%20from%20her%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Dr.%20Hamdan%20Abdullah%20Hamed%20first%20rented%20his%20Dubai%20villa%20on%20Airbnb%2C%20he%20left%20his%20food%20in%20the%20cupboards%2C%20assuming%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20came%20back%2C%20my%20stores%20were%20bare%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20sheets%2C%20towels%2C%20and%20even%20pillows%20were%20missing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Expecting%20a%20hotel%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20description%20of%20her%20flat%20states%20there%20will%20not%20be%20a%20daily%20room%20refresh%20or%20a%20full%20breakfast%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20Arrowsmith's%20guests%20often%20expect%20it.%20She%20also%20said%20guests%20have%20asked%20to%20be%20greeted%20at%20%26quot%3Bsilly%20o'clock%26quot%3B%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArrowsmith%20said%20she%20reminds%20Airbnb%20guests%20that%20they're%20%26quot%3Bstaying%20in%20a%20serviced%20apartment%2C%20not%20a%20hotel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20hotel%20services%2C%20stay%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you%20expect%20me%20to%20meet%20you%20at%202%20a.m.%2C%20then%20expect%20me%20to%20charge%20you%20more%20or%20go%20to%20a%20hotel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamed%20received%20a%20complaint%20from%20guests%20staying%20at%20his%20Airbnb%20property%20because%20it%20wasn't%20wheelchair%20accessible.%20Airbnb%20policy%20states%20that%20all%20reasonable%20accommodations%20for%20accessibility%20need%20to%20be%20discussed%20before%20the%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20no%20point%20did%20I%20ever%20state%20we%20have%20wheelchair%20accessibility%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamed%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Burning%20through%20gas%20and%20electricity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20price%20of%20gas%20and%20electricity%20soars%2C%20hosts%20find%20it%20frustrating%20when%20guests%20use%20either%20excessively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArrowsmith%20has%20experienced%20guests%20%26quot%3Bleaving%20all%20the%20windows%20open%20while%20putting%20the%20heat%20on%20full%20blast.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWould%20they%20be%20so%20wasteful%20with%20power%20paying%20their%20own%20bills%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Morgan%20owns%20a%20property%20in%20Anglesey%2C%20Wales%2C%20and%20started%20receiving%20calls%20last%20year%20from%20concerned%20neighbors%20about%20guests%20hanging%20wires%20out%20of%20windows%20to%20charge%20their%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20worked%20out%20that%20charging%20vehicles%20from%20her%20property%20added%20as%20much%20as%20%C2%A3600%20to%20her%20electricity%20bill.%20She%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Btotal%20lack%20of%20regard%26quot%3B%20for%20electricity%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Being%20a%20'professional%20complainer'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20four%20years%20of%20hosting%2C%20Fonseca%20has%20come%20across%20a%20few%20people%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%20complainers%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20guests%20who%20try%20to%20find%20issues%20to%20get%20refunds%20or%20discounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20multiple%20five-star%20reviews%2C%20there%20was%20one%20guest%20who%20complained%20about%20his%20house%20being%20dirty%20and%20smelling%20of%20cigarette%20smoke%2C%20even%20though%20they%20could%20provide%20no%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20rang%20Airbnb%20to%20say%20about%20the%20unfair%20review%2C%20they%20sided%20with%20the%20complainant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20of%20Fonseca's%20guests%20moved%20furniture%20and%20stripped%20beds%20%26quot%3Blooking%20for%20faults.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20couldn't%20find%20anything%20except%20for%20a%20picture%20frame%20underneath%20one%20of%20the%20beds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20took%20a%20picture%20of%20it%20and%20said%20there%20was%20rubbish%20under%20the%20beds.%20They%20ended%20up%20getting%20their%20refund.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-airbnb-gues