he%20company%20told%20Insider%20by%20email.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20committed%20to%20consistently%20evaluating%20the%20model%20to%20ensure%20it%20continues%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20our%20employees%20and%20the%20business%3B%20however%2C%20we%20are%20pleased%20with%20the%20results%20to%20date.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jif%20peanut%20butter%20pbj%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee2f922dfb7800199fdead%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJ.M.%20Smucker%20is%20the%20manufacturer%20of%20many%20well-known%20products%20like%20Jif%20peanut%20butter%20and%20Smucker's%20jam.%3Cp%3EFacebook%2FJif%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20about%206%2C000%20employees%20worldwide%2C%20but%20the%20%26quot%3Bcore%26quot%3B%20weeks%20program%20is%20targeted%20at%20the%201%2C300%20corporate%20workers%20based%20at%20its%20Orrville%20headquarters.%20Employees%20are%20asked%20to%20come%20into%20Orrville's%20campus%20for%20at%20least%20six%20days%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20or%2025%25%20of%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20during%20those%20core%20weeks%2C%20Journal%20said.%20Aside%20from%20that%20required%20time%2C%20they're%20allowed%20to%20be%20based%20anywhere%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20many%20employees%20continue%20to%20drive%20into%20the%20Orrville%20headquarters%20from%20nearby%20cities%2C%20the%20program%20has%20also%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20group%20of%20%26quot%3Bsuper-commuters%26quot%3B%20who%20live%20all%20over%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Journal%20noted.%20The%20company%20usually%20publishes%20its%20core%20week%20schedule%20a%20year%20in%20advance%20to%20give%20its%20employees%20time%20to%20plan%20their%20office%20visits%2C%20the%20Journal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicole%20Massey%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20marketing%20who%20oversees%20the%20company's%20consumer%20foods%20division%2C%20lives%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20but%20commutes%20to%20Orrville%20for%20core%20weeks%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Journal's%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20travel%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Massey%20told%20the%20Journal%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20really%20feel%20I'm%20home%20and%20present%20actually%20much%20more%20than%20I%20would%20be%20if%20I%20was%20working%20at%20a%20company%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20and%20commuting%20even%20three%20days%20a%20week.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20still%20a%20small%20number%20of%20salaried%20employees%2C%20like%20food%20scientists%20who%20need%20specialized%20equipment%2C%20who%20come%20in%20five%20days%20a%20week.%20the%20Journal%20said.%20The%20300%20or%20so%20employees%20who%20work%20in%20the%20company's%20manufacturing%20division%20%E2%80%94%20which%20produces%20its%20jams%2C%20jellies%2C%20and%20ice%20cream%20toppings%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20also%20don't%20participate%20in%20core%20weeks%2C%20the%20Journal%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Smucker%2C%20the%20company's%20CEO%20and%20a%20fifth-generation%20member%20of%20the%20founding%20family%2C%20commutes%2040%20minutes%20into%20the%20Orrville%20campus%20from%20his%20home%20in%20Akron%2C%20Ohio%2C%20on%20most%20days%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Journal.%20%26quot%3BThe%20relationships%20get%20built%20in%20between%20meetings%2C%20not%20during%20meetings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20Journal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDoes%20your%20company%20have%20a%20return-to-office%20policy%20that%20you%20think%20is%20working%E2%80%94%20or%20failing%3F%20We%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Contact%20reporter%20Lakshmi%20Varanasi%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Elvaranasi%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmuckers-employees-office-few-days-a-month-during-core-weeks-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%