%20Price%20Inflation%20Dragged%20Down%20Real%20Wages%20of%20Gig%20Workers%20in%202022%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F22122808%2FZomato_Swiggy_PTI1-1200.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERising%20fuel%20costs%20and%20consumer%20price%20inflation%20led%20to%20an%2011%25%20fall%20in%20the%20real%20wages%20of%20gig%20workers%20per%20month%20in%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fpolicy%2Feconomy-fuel-cost-inflation-drag-real-wages-of-gig-workers-in-2022-3226951%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20a%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20study%20by%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Applied%20Economic%20Research%20(NCAER)%2C%20real%20wages%20of%20gig%20workers%20fell%2011%25%20to%20Rs%2011%2C963%20per%20month%20in%202022%20as%20compared%20to%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20nominal%20income%20of%20the%20surveyed%20food%20delivery%20workers%20went%20up%20by%204%25%20to%20Rs%2020%2C026%20in%202022%2C%20from%20Rs%2019%2C239%20per%20month%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20nominal%20wages%20are%20not%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%2C%20whereas%20real%20wages%20are%20adjusted%20for%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20covered%20924%20food%20delivery%20workers%20and%20found%20that%20the%20real%20wages%20of%20gig%20workers%20delivering%20food%20parcels%20across%20cities%20have%20fallen.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20performance%20of%20foodtech%20platforms%20in%20terms%20of%20unit%20economics%20has%20improved%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20net%20incomes%20definitely%20decreased%20because%20of%20the%20high%20input%20cost%20of%20fuel%20and%20rising%20inflation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bornali%20Bhandari%2C%20who%20lead%20the%20study%20at%20the%20NCAER%2C%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20one%20hand%2C%20it%20has%20become%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20achieve%20daily%2Fweekly%20targets%20over%20time%2C%20which%20affects%20their%20ability%20to%20earn%20additional%20income%20from%20incentives%3B%20this%20was%20due%20to%20increased%20traffic%20and%20greater%20competition.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20fuel%20costs%20had%20gone%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20fuel%20costs%20and%20overall%20inflation%20started%20to%20rise%2C%20workers%20found%20it%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20meet%20monthly%20expenditure%20from%20their%20monthly%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693386033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F22122808%2FZomato_Swiggy_PTI1-1200.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frising-fuel-costs-consumer-price-inflation-dragged-down-real-wages-of-gig-workers-in-2022-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Real%20wages%20of%20gig%20workers%20fell%2011%25%20to%20Rs%2011%2C963%20per%20month%20in%202022%20as%20compared%20to%202019%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20by%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Applied%20Economic%20Research.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frising-fuel-costs-consumer-price-inflation-dragged-down-real-wages-of-gig-workers-in-2022-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20is%20killing%20the%20grand%20bargain%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20web.%20'We're%20in%20a%20different%20world.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223113%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI%20screenwriter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F645957d065a21600192faf6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221828%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20screenwriter%3Cp%3EMoor%20Studio%2FGetty%20Images%20Plus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EContent%20