nt%20into%20this%20exercise%20thinking%20McDonald's%2C%20which%20has%20been%20serving%20breakfast%20since%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcorpmcd%2Four-stories%2Farticle%2Fegg-mcmuffin-history.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1977%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20have%20the%20advantage%20of%20taste%20and%20presentation.%20But%20I%20also%20thought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwendys-breakfast-menu-chicken-sandwich-compete-chick-fil-a-2020-2%5C%22%3EWendy's%2C%20which%20launched%20breakfast%20in%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20could%20win%20on%20price%20if%20the%20food%20was%20halfway%20edible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20the%20contest%20wasn't%20even%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20I%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFast-food%20breakfast%20has%20long%20been%20dominated%20by%20McDonald's.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20Egg%20McMuffin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eccbb910a2ec00199f4f2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20McDonald's%20Egg%20McMuffin%20is%20displayed%20at%20a%20McDonald's%20restaurant%20on%20July%2023%2C%202015%20in%20Fairfield%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201975%2C%20McDonald's%20launched%20the%20Egg%20McMuffin%20nationally%20after%20testing%20the%20breakfast%20sandwich%20for%20a%20few%20years.%20The%20success%20of%20the%20Egg%20McMuffin%20led%20McDonald's%20to%20roll%20out%20its%20first%20breakfast%20line%20in%20US%20stores%20in%201977.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20menu%20included%20the%20Egg%20McMuffin%2C%20hotcakes%2C%20toasted%20English%20muffins%2C%20scrambled%20eggs%2C%20sausage%2C%20hash%20browns%2C%20and%20a%20Danish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Dunkin'%20and%20Starbucks%2C%20McDonald's%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20fan%20favorite%2C%20the%20market-research%20firm%20Technomic%20found%20in%20recent%20consumer%20data.%20Wendy's%20hasn't%20really%20gained%20much%20ground%20on%20McDonald's%20since%20introducing%20breakfast%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Wendy's%20is%20enjoying%20growth%20during%20the%20breakfast%20daypart%2C%20I%20would%20argue%20that%20they%20are%20not%20taking%20breakfast%20share%20from%20McDonald's%2C%26quot%3B%20Robert%20Byrne%2C%20the%20director%20of%20consumer%20and%20industry%20insights%20at%20Technomic%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BOur%20data%20suggests%20that%20they%20are%20growing%20more%20competitive%20with%20other%20options%20such%20as%20c-stores%20or%20at-home%20morning%20occasions.%20I%20would%20also%20suggest%20they%20may%20be%20chipping%20away%20at%20more%20expensive%20breakfast%20players%2C%20such%20as%20Panera.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcorpmcd%2Four-stories%2Farticle%2Fegg-mcmuffin-history.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20Technomic.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20brands%20such%20as%20Wendy's%2C%20Burger%20King%2C%20and%20Taco%20Bell%20have%20tried%20to%20steal%20market%20share%20from%20the%20Golden%20Arches.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20window%20of%20a%20Wendy's%20restaurant%20showing%20two%20promotional%20posters%20for%20its%20breakfast%20menu.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6192d8688e9bfa0019870fd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20breakfast%20promotion%20at%20Wendy's.%3Cp%3EMary%20Meisenzahl%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWendy's%20is%20serious%20about%20beating%20McDonald's%20at%20breakfast.%20The%20chain%20came%20out%20fighting%20when%20it%20launched%20breakfast%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFans%20could%20%26quot%3Bsay%20goodbye%20to%20their%20tired%2C%20old%2C%20stale%20breakfast%20and%20instead%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20a%20selection%20of%20fresh%2C%20craveable%2C%20bold%20new%20morning%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irwendys.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-details%2F2020%2FWendys-Introduces-A-Better-Breakfast-Asks-America-You-Up-For-This%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echain%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EItems%20on%20the%20debut%20breakfast%20menu%20included%20the%20Breakfast%20Baconator%2C%20Honey%20Butter%20Chicken%20Biscuit%2C%20and%20Frosty-ccino.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20pandemic%20forced%20some%20restaurant%20chains%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nrn.com%2Fquick-service%2Ftaco-bell-ceo-mark-king-covid-19-crisis-accelerating-future%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaco%20Bell%20to%20put%20breakfast%20on%20pause%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20three%20years%20later%2C%20Wendy's%20is%20still%20betting%20big%20on%20breakfast.%20They've%20added%20more%20items%20and%20have%20been%20pushing%20value%20deals%20to%20entice%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20breakfast%20sales%20at%20Wendy's%20account%20for%207%25%20of%20gross%20sales%2C%20Technomic%20indicates%2C%20citing%20the%20chain's%20latest%20franchise%20disclosure%20document.%20And%20that's%20on%20the%20low%20end%2C%20data%20from%20the%20restaurant-consulting%20firm%20Foodservice%20IP%20suggests.%20Fast-food%20breakfast%20sales%20typically%20range%20between%205%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20total%20sales%2C%20the%20firm%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWendy's%20latest%20push%20is%20a%20two-for-%243%20breakfast%20bundle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWendy's%20two-for-%243%20meal%20bundle%20includes%20these%20choices%3A%20a%20sausage%20biscuit%2C%20an%20egg%20and%20cheese%20biscuit%2C%20small%20seasoned%20potatoes%2C%20or%20a%20medium%20hot%20coffee.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3