howing%20two%20of%20the%20breakfast%20deals.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecd222ecb92e0019255823%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20order%20every%20item%20in%20the%20bundled%20meal%20deal%20that%20equaled%20%243%2C%20but%20the%20cashier%20didn't%20seem%20to%20understand%20my%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20mentioned%20%26quot%3BBiggie%20Bundles%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20clueless.%20Finally%2C%20we%20settled%20on%20the%20following%20two-for-%243%20orders%3A%20the%20sausage%20biscuit%20and%20the%20egg%20%26amp%3B%20cheese%20biscuit%20for%20%243%3B%20and%20the%20coffee%20and%20seasoned%20potatoes%20for%20%243.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20order%20any%20other%20combinations%2C%20but%20obviously%2C%20someone%20can%20also%20order%20a%20sausage%20biscuit%20and%20potatoes%20for%20%243%20or%20a%20cheese%20biscuit%20and%20coffee%20for%20%243%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFirst%20up%2C%20the%20sausage%20biscuit.%20This%20is%20a%20no-nonsense%2C%20as-plain-as-it-gets%20breakfast%20sandwich.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20biscuit%20with%20a%20square%20sausage%20patty%20in%20the%20middle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecd3e19d7fd30019837e3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20sausage%20stuffed%20in%20a%20flaky%20biscuit.%20I%20love%20how%20the%20sausage%20is%20square%3B%20a%20very%20on-brand%20move%20for%20Wendy's%20to%20mimic%20the%20shape%20of%20its%20famous%20beef%20patties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sausage%20patty%20was%20flavorful.%20I%20could%20taste%20a%20mix%20of%20herbs%20and%20spices%20such%20as%20black%20pepper%20and%20sage%2C%20leaving%20a%20spicy%20aftertaste.%20The%20sausage%20worked%20well%20with%20the%20biscuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20a%20golden-brown%20biscuit%2C%20but%20it%20had%20the%20right%20texture.%20It%20was%20flaky%20and%20buttery%20on%20the%20outside%20and%20moist%20on%20the%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWendy's%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiscuits%20come%20from%20a%20trusted%20supplier%2C%20and%20are%20baked%20fresh%20throughout%20the%20morning%20in%20each%20restaurant.%20They%20are%20made%20with%20real%20buttermilk%20for%20a%20buttery%20and%20flaky%20bite.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHot%20take%20on%20value%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20regular%20price%20of%20an%20%C3%A0%20la%20carte%20sausage%20biscuit%20at%20the%20restaurant%20I%20visited%20in%20Orange%2C%20California%20was%20%242.99.%20So%2C%20at%20the%20current%20value%20deal%2C%20this%20sandwich%20was%20essentially%20marked%20down%2050%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20egg%20and%20cheese%20biscuit%20came%20next.%20The%20most%20noticeable%20part%20of%20this%20sandwich%20was%20the%20paper-thin%20egg%20it%20was%20stuffed%20with.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Wendy's%20egg%20and%20cheese%20biscuit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecd4c03c42320019c0174d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20egg%20looked%20like%20a%20round%20Egg%20McMuffin-inspired%20egg%20if%20someone%20had%20stepped%20on%20it.%20It%20was%20super%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20egg%20was%20topped%20with%20a%20bright%20orange%20slice%20of%20cheese%20that%20wasn't%20melted.%20The%20egg%20and%20the%20cheese%20flopped%20over%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20biscuit%2C%20which%20was%20visually%20appealing.%20It%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20getting%20a%20hefty%20sandwich%20despite%20the%20paper-thin%20egg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHot%20take%20on%20val