peg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20gave%20up%20coffee%20in%20early%20December%202022%20after%20a%20bout%20with%20COVID-19.%20Even%20though%20it's%20been%20months%20since%20I've%20sipped%20on%20a%20hot%20cup%20of%20Joe%2C%20I%20know%20what%20good%20coffee%20should%20taste%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20drink%20about%20two%20to%20three%20cups%20of%20coffee%20or%20espresso%20in%20the%20morning.%20And%20we're%20talking%20the%20good%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20Lavazza%20and%20Illycaff%C3%A8.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20Wendy's%20coffee%20passable%20for%20fast-food%20java.%20But%20it%20had%20a%20slightly%20burned%20taste.%20It%20could%20be%20a%20brewing%20issue%20or%20a%20sourcing%20issue.%20Wendy's%20sources%20its%20beans%20from%20Rainforest%20Alliance%20Certified%20farms%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHot%20take%20on%20value%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20medium%20coffee%20cost%20%241.79%20at%20the%20restaurant%20I%20visited.%20Of%20all%20four%20items%20on%20the%20bundle%20list%2C%20this%20one%20had%20the%20least%20savings%20at%20about%2029%20cents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20was%20surprisingly%20delighted%20with%20the%20Wendy's%20breakfast%20value%20options.%20The%20biscuits%20were%20flaky%2C%20and%20the%20crispy%20potatoes%20tasted%20like%20a%20side%20order%20you'd%20get%20at%20a%20full-service%20breakfast%20diner.%20It%20elevated%20the%20meal%20compared%20to%20a%20standard%20hash%20brown.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221115%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%202%20for%20%243%20Biggie%20Bundles%20deal%20promotional%20image.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecd7ed3c42320019c01be9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22836%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWendy's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20solid%20fast-food%20value%20deal%20because%20you%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20and%20the%20food%20quality%20is%20decent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recommend%20this%20menu%20hack%3A%20Buy%20the%20two%20biscuit%20sandwiches%20for%20%243%20and%20add%20the%20sausage%20to%20the%20egg%20and%20cheese%20biscuit.%20There's%20a%20sausage%2C%20egg%2C%20and%20cheese%20biscuit%20on%20the%20Wendy's%20menu%20for%20%243.99.%20So%2C%20you'll%20save%20about%20%241%20if%20you%20do%20it%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20save%20the%20second%20biscuit%20for%20breakfast%20the%20next%20morning.%20Just%20add%20some%20jam%20and%20butter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20drove%20less%20than%20two%20miles%20to%20McDonald's%20to%20try%20and%20replicate%20the%20meal%20I%20had%20at%20Wendy's.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nancy%20Luna%20takes%20a%20selfie%20in%20front%20of%20a%20McDonald's%20sign.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecda15ecb92e00192561e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20walked%20into%20a%20very%20modern%20McDonald's%20that%20had%20only%20two%20cash%20registers%20for%20taking%20orders.%20Only%20one%20worker%20was%20taking%20orders%20at%209%20a.m.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Wendy's%2C%20where%20I%20was%20the%20only%20customer%2C%20this%20McDonald's%20had%20about%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20in%20the%20dining%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20order%20from%20one%20of%20three%20kiosks%20in%20the%20store%2C%20so%20I%20could%20take%20my%20time%20with%20my%20order.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20kiosks%20were%20easy%20to%20navigate%2C%20making%20for%20a%20frictionless%20ordering%20process%20compared%20to%20my%20Wendy's%20experience%20with%20the%20cashier%20who%20had%20trouble%20understanding%20my%20order.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20kiosks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecdb1fecb92e001925636d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20filtered%20for%20biscuit%20sandwiches.%20I%20found%20a%20sausage%20biscuit%20menu%20item%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20as%20the%20one%20at%20Wendy's%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20ordered%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20doesn't%20have%20a%20biscuit%20cheese%20and%20egg%20sandwich.%20The%20only%20thing%20that%20came%20close%20was%20the%20bacon%2C%20egg%2C%20and%20cheese%20biscuit%20sandwich.%20So%20I%20ordered%20that%20and%20removed%20the%20bacon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kiosk%20made%20this%20customization%20very%20easy%2C%20but%20please%20note%20the%20sandwich%20still%20cost%20the%20same%2C%20%244.19%2C%20even%20with%20the%20bacon%20removed.%20I%20then%20ordered%20a%20medium%20coffee%20and%20a%20hash%20brown.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHot%20take%20on%20value%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Right%20away%2C%20it's%20obvious%20how%20cheap%20Wendy's%20new%20breakfast%20deal%20is.%20My%20McDonald's%20check%20was%20%2412.24.%20For%20%246%20plus%20tax%2C%20I%20got%20nearly%20the%20same%20four%20items%20by%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20two-for-%243%20Biggie%20Bundles%20deal%20at%20Wendy's.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20the%20McDonald's%20I%20visited%20was%20offering%20a%20two-for-%245.50%20breakfast%20deal%20that%20included%20two%20Sausage%20McMuffins%20with%20egg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20tried%20was%20the%20sausage%20biscuit.%20In%20terms%20of%20presentation%2C%20it%20looked%20better%20than%20Wendy's%20as%20the%20biscuit%20had%20a%20beautiful%20golden%20crust.%20But%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20it%20was%20spongy%20and%20flavorless.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20McDonald's%20sausage%20biscuit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecdeb93c42320019c024ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2Finsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biscuit%20and%20sausage%20looked%20limp%20like%20it%20had%20been%20sitting%20under%20a%20heat%20lamp%20for%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biscuit%20was%20not%20flaky%20at%20all.%20When%20I%20bit%20into%20the%20sandwich%2C%20the%20biscuit%20felt%20rubbery%20and%20spongy.%20It%20was%20thick%20and%20absorbent.%20I%20probably%20could%20have%20used%20it%20to%20wipe%20up%20a%20coffee%20spill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sausage%20was%20greasy%20and%20flavorless%20like%20it%20had%20just%20been%20thawed%20from%20frozen%2C%20heated%20up%20in%20a%20microwave%2C%20and%20slapped%20onto%20the%20biscuit.%20Overall%2C%20it%20was%20disappointing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHot%20take%20on%20value%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20sausage%20biscuit%20at%20the%20McDonald's%20in%20Orange%20cost%20%242.19.%20The%20same%20sandwich%20at%20Wendy's%20cost%20%242.99.%20But%2C%20if%20you%20order%20Wendy's%20sausage%20biscuit%20as%20part%20of%20the%20two-for-%243%20value%20deal%2C%20it's%20essentially%20%241.50.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Egg%20and%20Cheese%20Biscuit%20came%20with%20a%20beautiful%20folded%20egg.%20Sadly%2C%20that%20was%20the%20best%20part%20of%20this%20sandwich.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221079%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20McDonald's%20egg%20and%20cheese%20biscuit%20with%20a%20folded%20egg.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecdf743c42320019c025ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22809%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20Wendy's%20biscuit%2C%20the%20cheese%20on%20this%20sandwich%20was%20fully%20melted%20on%20the%20biscuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20being%20layered%20with%20a%20freshly%20cracked%20Egg%20McMuffin-style%20round%20egg%2C%20the%20biscuit%20came