%20Pugalia%2C%20the%20minister%20was%20asked%20about%20global%20%26quot%3Btalk%20shops%26quot%3B%20and%20western%20countries%20lecturing%20India%20without%20knowing%20how%20the%20country%20is%20taking%20various%20steps%2C%20like%20being%20on%20the%20path%20to%20becoming%20the%20number%20one%20nation%20in%20the%20use%20of%20solar%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20he%20agreed%20that%20there%20is%2C%20sometimes%2C%20too%20much%20talk%20in%20talk%20shops%20and%20people%20who%20lecture%20others%20don't%20practice%20what%20they%20preach.%20He%20said%2C%20however%2C%20that%20he%20is%20not%20against%20talking%20because%20debate%20and%20discussions%20are%20the%20way%20to%20take%20things%20forward.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20what%20we%20should%20do%20is%20through%20our%20actions%20and%20through%20our%20example...%20when%20India%20increases%20the%20use%20of%20renewables%2C%20when%20we%20demonstrate%20how%20big%20a%20change%20can%20happen%20through%20the%20use%20of%20LED%20bulbs%2C%20we%20are%20also%20talking%20seriously%20about%20electric%20mobility...%20so%20we%20also%20have%20to%20show%20the%20world%20through%20our%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20debate%20in%20debating%20forums%2C%20we%20should%20not%20leave%20the%20battlefield%20there.%20In%20Paris%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20there%20would%20be%20an%20annual%20commitment%20of%20100%20billion%20dollars.%20That%20hasn't%20happened%2C%20but%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20repeating%20it%20to%20make%20people%20feel%20ashamed.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20told%20this%20was%20their%20promise%20and%20they%20didn't%20fulfil%20it.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20here%2C%20we%20are%20not%20alone%2C%20we%20have%20125%20countries%20with%20us%2C%20whom%20we%20call%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20global%20south%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20India%20is%20a%20developing%20country%20and%2C%20because%20it%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20being%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20global%20south%20is%20its%20responsibility.%20He%20asserted%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20responsibility%20that%20India%20has%20assigned%20to%20itself%2C%20but%20it%20has%20consulted%20125%20countries.%20He%20said%20no%20other%20G20%20chair%20went%20through%20the%20exercise%20of%20talking%20to%20125%20countries%20and%20asking%20them%20what%20their%20worries%20are%20because%20they%20are%20not%20on%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20putting%20issues%20forward%20on%20their%20behalf%20is%20very%20central.%20And%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20climate%2C%20because%20the%20climate%20situation%20is%20getting%20worse.%20We%20are%20seeing%20it%20in%20our%20country%2C%20our%20neighbourhood%2C%20across%20the%20world.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20different%20department.%20We%20have%20to%20remember%20this%20is%20a%20globalised%20world.%20Today%2C%20climate%20emergencies%2C%20climate%20disasters%2C%20because%20they%20are%20happening%20more%20regularly%2C%20more%20strongly%2C%20they%20have%20become%20a%20major%20economic%20disruptor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20problems%20with%20the%20way%20globalisation%20is%20today%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20is%20that%20things%20are%20produced%20in%20different%20places%20and%20if%20supply%20chains%20are%20interrupted%20because%20of%20climate%20factors%2C%20the%20whole%20economy%20can%20be%20jeopardised%20by%20climate%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693385520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fjhlut638_s-jaishankar-told-ndtv_625x300_29_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-just-talk-india-has-led-by-example-on-climate-change-s-jaishankar-4341839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20nothing%20against%20talking%2C%20but%20it%20should%2C%20and%20has%2C%20led%20by%20example%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20combat%20climate%20change%2C%20External%20A