4341856%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Key%20Lok%20Sabha%20Panel%20Asks%20Speaker%20To%20Revoke%20Congress%20Leader's%20Suspension%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Privileges%20Committee%20of%20Parliament%20has%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20to%20revoke%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury's%20suspension%20from%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20recommended%20this%20to%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chowdhury%2C%20Congress's%20leader%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20was%20suspended%20during%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20motion%20for%20his%20suspension%20was%20moved%20by%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi.%20%26quot%3BThis%20House%20having%20taken%20the%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20gross%2C%20deliberate%20and%20repeated%20misconduct%20of%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20in%20utter%20disregard%20to%20the%20House%20and%20authority%20of%20Chair%20resolves%20that%20the%20matter%20of%20his%20misconduct%20be%20referred%20to%20Committee%20of%20Privileges%20of%20the%20House%20for%20the%20further%20investigation%20and%20report%20to%20the%20House%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20be%20suspended%20from%20the%20service%20of%20the%20House%20till%20the%20Committee%20submits%20its%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Privileges%20Committee%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20was%20unanimous%20in%20adopting%20the%20resolution%20to%20revoke%20Mr%20Chowdhury's%20suspension.%20The%20committee%20is%20led%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Singh.%20BJP%20members%20in%20the%20committee%20also%20supported%20the%20resolution.%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20had%20appeared%20before%20the%20panel%20and%20told%20the%20members%20that%20he%20had%20no%20intention%20to%20offend%20anyone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20suspension%2C%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20had%20told%20the%20media%20that%20he%20had%20no%20intention%20to%20insult%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20mean%20to%20offend%20anyone.%20I%20have%20not%20said%20anything%20wrong%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20ji%20is%20sitting%20'nirav'%20on%20Manipur%20issue%2C%20which%20means%20sitting%20silent.%20'Nirav'%20means%20to%20be%20silent.%20My%20intention%20was%20not%20to%20insult%20PM%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20did%20not%20feel%20that%20he%20was%20insulted%2C%20his%20darbaris%20(courtiers)%20felt%20so%20and%20brought%20this%20proposal%20against%20me.%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20(the%20matter)%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20privileges%20committee%20and%20I%20have%20been%20suspended%20till%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20MP%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20then%20hit%20out%20at%20its%20leader's%20suspension%2C%20calling%20the%20move%20%26quot%3Bundemocratic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693384680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F371e2mtg_adhir-ranjan-chowdhary_625x300_19_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadhir-ranjan-chowdhury-lok-sabha-privileges-committee-key-lok-sabha-panel-asks-speaker-to-revoke-congress-leaders-suspension-4341893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Privileges%20Committee%20of%20Parliament%20has%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20to%20revoke%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury's%20suspension%20from%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20recommended%20this%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadhir-ranjan-chowdhury-lok-sabha-privileges-committee-key-lok-sabha-panel-asks-speaker-to-revoke-congress-leaders-suspension-4341893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadhir-ranjan-chowdhury-lok-sabha-privileges-committee-key-lok-sabha-panel-asks-speaker-to-revoke-co