-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fsports%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-interfere-with-punjab-and-haryana-high-court-order-staying-wfi-polls%2Fcid%2F1962410%5C%22%3Edismissed%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Amateur%20Wrestling%20Association%E2%80%99s%20plea%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20lift%20the%20interim%20order%20staying%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20elections%20that%20were%20to%20be%20held%20on%20August%2012%20were%20put%20on%20hold%20by%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20on%20August%2011%20after%20the%20Haryana%20Amateur%20Wrestling%20Association%20moved%20the%20court%20asking%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20election%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Abhay%20S.%20Oka%20and%20Pankaj%20Mithal%20asked%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20association%20to%20approach%20the%20high%20court%20with%20its%20grievances%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fsports%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-interfere-with-punjab-and-haryana-high-court-order-staying-wfi-polls%2Fcid%2F1962410%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20we%20entertain%20this%3F%20You%20go%20to%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%A6%20Instead%20of%20applying%20for%20vacating%20the%20interim%20stay%2C%20the%20petitioner%20has%20chosen%20to%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20We%2C%20therefore%2C%20decline%20to%20entertain%20this%20special%20leave%20petition%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said%20and%20granted%20the%20petitioner%20liberty%20to%20seek%20impleadment%20as%20a%20party%20in%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20apex%20court%20also%20asked%20the%20high%20court%20to%20give%20necessary%20priority%20to%20the%20case%2C%20if%20the%20petitioner%20files%20a%20plea%20for%20impleadment%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAttorney%20General%20R.%20Venkataramani%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20said%20that%20the%20petitioner%20has%20bypassed%20the%20high%20court%20and%20jumped%20directly%20to%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20was%20told%20by%20the%20association%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20that%20WFI%20had%20been%20de-recognised%20by%20the%20United%20World%20Wrestling%20(UWW)%20and%20it%20was%20an%20embarrassment%20for%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20global%20wrestling%20body%E2%80%99s%20decision%20came%20after%20the%20election%20process%20failed%20to%20take%20place%20in%20time.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Indian%20wrestlers%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20at%20the%20upcoming%20championships%20under%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20flag%20and%20would%20have%20to%20participate%20as%20%E2%80%98neutral%20athletes%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20election%20process%20should%20not%20be%20stopped.%20We%20have%20no%20axe%20to%20grind%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20association%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association-appointed%20ad-hoc%20panel%20governing%20the%20WFI%20had%20initially%20scheduled%20the%20elections%20for%20July%206%20which%20were%20then%20rescheduled%20to%20July%2011%20after%20disaffiliated%20state%20bodies%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20approached%20it%20for%20a%20hearing%2C%20claiming%20their%20dismissal%20was%20not%20appropriate%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20polls%20w