20after%20a%20special%20function%20held%20at%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20where%20a%20commemorative%20coin%20on%20N.T.%20Rama%20Rao%20was%20released%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20his%20birth%20centenary%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20NTR%2C%20founded%20TDP%20after%20achieving%20stardom%20in%20Telugu%20cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fat-release-of-ntr-coin-wife-not-present%5C%22%3ECentre%20Unveils%20Special%20Coin%20on%20NTR%3A%20A%20Political%20Message%20in%20Dropping%20His%20Wife%20from%20the%20Guest%20List%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fspeculations-of-possible-alliance-between-tdp-and-bjp-sparked-by-meeting-between-naidu-and-nadda-101693336504555.html%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BJP%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20D.%20Purandeshwari%20and%20her%20husband%20Duggubati%20Venkateswara%20Rao%2C%20a%20former%20MLA%2C%20were%20also%20present%20during%20the%20discussion.%20The%20meeting%20is%20said%20to%20have%20lasted%20for%2015%20to%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpurandeswari-andhra-pradesh-bjp-chief-tdp-growth%5C%22%3EPurandeshwari%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Union%20minister%20in%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%2C%20has%20been%20recently%20made%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20unit%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Purandeshwari%20is%20a%20daughter%20of%20NTR%2C%20and%20Naidu%20is%20married%20to%20her%20sister%2C%20Bhuvaneshwari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20a%20possible%20pact%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20Naidu%20said%20it%20would%20be%20decided%20at%20an%20%E2%80%9Cappropriate%20time%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20comment%20about%20the%20alliances%20now.%20We%20haven%E2%80%99t%20yet%20decided%20on%20the%20parties%20that%20we%20will%20be%20allying%20with.%20Discussions%20are%20on%20and%20a%20decision%20on%20alliances%20will%20be%20taken%20at%20an%20appropriate%20time%20as%20we%20assess%20the%20situation%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fandhrapradesh%2Fchandrababu-naidu-drops-hints-that-tdp-is-still-open-for-alliance%2F%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Naidu%20as%20saying%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20also%20sought%20to%20convey%20that%20his%20party%20snapped%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20in%202018%20only%20on%20the%20question%20of%20Special%20Category%20Status%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20In%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20TDP%20had%20allied%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20attempted%20to%20form%20a%20joint%20front%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP.%20After%20TDP%20faced%20its%20worst%20defeat%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20and%20parliament%20elections%2C%20however%2C%20Naidu%20has%20distanced%20himself%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20his%20meeting%20with%20Nadda%2C%20Naidu%20said%20that%20he%20is%20not%20opposed%20to%20supporting%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%20%E2%80%9Cnation-building%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%E2%80%9COtherwise%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20serious%20differences%20with%20the%20Centre.%20I%20have%20made%20it%20clear%20several%20times%20in%20the%20past%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20TDP%20has%20been%20making%20overtures%20to%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20past%20several%20months%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20towards%20its%20former%20ally%20has%20been%20sending%20confusing%20signals.%20The%20TDP%20has%20been%20advocating%20for%20a%20grand%20alliance%20of%20sorts%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20with%20Pawan%20Kalyan-led%20Jana%20Sena%20and%20BJP%20to%20take%20on%20the%20ruling%20YSR%20Congress%20Party.%20Both%20Jana%20Sena%20and%20TDP%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20should%20come%20together%20to%20avoid%20anti-government%20from%20splitting.%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20goes%20to%20assembly%20polls%20in%20another%20eight%20months%20along%20with%20parliament%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20week%20of%20July%20when%20NDA%20held%20its%20first%20meeting%20of%20its%20allies%20and%20potential%20allies%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20polls%20in%20the%20second%20week%20of%20July%2C%20Jana%20Sena%20received%20an%20invitation%2C%20but%20TDP%20did%20not.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20was%20weeks%20after%20Naidu%20had%20called%20on%20BJP%20leader%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20June.%20The%20Naidu-Shah%20meeting%20at%20that%20time%20had%20sparked%20intense%20speculation%20that%20the%20TDP%20and%20BJP%20alliance%20was%20now%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%20However%2C%20that%20was%20not%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20has%20a%20friendly%20relationship%20with%20the%20ruling%20YSR%20Congress%20in%20the%20state%20though%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20alliance%20in%20place.%20Both%20TDP%20and%20YSR%20Congress%20have%20been%20supportive%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20parliament%20during%20the%20passage%20of%20several%20Bills%2C%20including%20during%20the%20recent%20controversial%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill.%20They%20also%20stood%20by%20the%20BJP%20when%20the%2026-party%20INDIA%20bloc%20moved%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fat-release-of-ntr-coin-wife-not-present%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20announce%20any%20alliance%20with%20parties%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20release%20of%20a%20special%20coin%20on%20the%20NTR%20birth%20anniversary%20recently%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20is%20aimed%20at%20BJP%20wanting%20to%20associate%20itself%20with%20the%20legacy%20of%20NTR%2C%20which%20is%20now%20to%20the%20advantage%20of%20the%20TDP.%20The%20move%20to%20appoint%20NTR%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20Purandeswari%20as%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20BJP%20chief%20and%20the%20special%20coin%20on%20NTR%20are%20in%20that%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28182941%2FNTR-coin.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28182941%2FNTR-coin.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28182941%2FNTR-coin-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28182941%2FNTR-coin-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28182941%2FNTR-coin-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670322%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20Cultural%20Centre%20on%20August%2028.%20Photo%3A%20pib.gov.in%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSR%20Congress%E2%80%99%20response%20to%20the%20unveiling%20of%20the%20special%20coin%20on%20NTR%20and%20the%20Nadda-Naidu%20meeting%20has%20been%20interesting.%20It%20hit%20out%20at%20Purandeshwari%20for%20not%20extending%20an%20invitation%20to%20NTR%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Lakshmi%20Parvathy%2C%20who%20is%20the%20chairperson%20of%20Telugu%20Academy%20under%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20government.%20The%20official%20function%20held%20in%20Rashtrapathi%20Bhavan%20was%20attended%20by%20all%20family%20members%20of%20NTR%20except%20Parvathy.%20On%20the%20Nadda-Naidu%20meeting%2C%20it%20alleged%20that%20Purandeswari%20and%20her%20wife%20were%20lobbying%20for%20the%20BJP-TDP%20alliance%20though%20Nadda%20was%20reluctant%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20more%20evidence%20does%20it%20require%20to%20say%20that%20you%2C%20your%20husband%20and%20your%20brother-in-law%20%E2%80%93%20all%20l%20belong%20to%20the%20same%20clan.%20Even%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20knows%20about%20it.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20key%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20thief!%E2%80%9D%20YSR%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20V.%20Vijaya%20Sai%20Reddy%20tweeted%2C%20referring%20to%20Purandeshwari%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20as%20the%20state%20BJP%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENaidu%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20caste-based%20census%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Naidu%20has%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20caste-based%20census%2C%20which%20the%20opposition%20has%20been%20demanding%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20conduct.%20He%20said%20it%20will%20be%20of%20help%20in%20effective%20poverty%20alleviation%20in%20the%20country%2C%20by%20gathering%20data%20on%20the%20correct%20economic%20situation%20of%20all%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20poor%20people%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20benefitted%20from%20government%20policies%20in%20each%20section%2C%20whether%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20and%20even%20the%20forward%20caste%20groups.%20We%20need%20a%20comprehensive%20caste%20census%20and%20we%20must%20have%20a%20strategy%20based%20on%20the%20report%20on%20how%20to%20target%20these%20groups%20in%20particular%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fformer-ap-cm-chandrababu-naidu-supports-caste-based-census%2Farticle67248787.ece%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Naidu%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20problems%20with%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20as%20it%20is%20fundamentally%20at%20odds%20with%20its%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20seeking%20%E2%80%98vertical%20integration%E2%80%99%20of%20all%20castes%20under%20a%20Hindutva%20umbrella%20and%20also%20not%20suitable%20for%20it%20politically.%20It%20feels%20such%20a%20survey%20will%20only%20benefit%20the%20Opposition%20speaking%20of%20empowerment%20and%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693379383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30115308%2FThe-Wire-1-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-nadda-naidu-meeting-speculation-rife-again-over-tdp-bjp-possible-alliance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20TDP%20has%20been%20making%20overtures%20to%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20past%20several%20months%2C%20the%20BJP's%20attitude%20towards%20its%20former%20ally%20has%20been%20sending%20confusing%20signals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-nadda-naidu-meeting-speculation-rife-again-over-tdp-bjp-possible-alliance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20must%20ensure%20there's%20no%20spillover%20from%20surging%20food%20prices%3A%20MPC%20members%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693379270000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F04%2Ffull%2F1688454109-0348.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Frbi-must-ensure-there-s-no-spillover-from-surging-food-prices-mpc-members-123083000336_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20central%20bank%20is%20targeting%20to%20keep%20inflation%20between%202%25%20and%206%25%20but%20the%20consumer%20price%20index%20accelerated%20by%207.44%25%20last%20month%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2F