here%20was%20no%20need%20to%20worry%20if%20I%20took%20medicines%20on%20time.%20Treatment%20adherence%20is%20important%20to%20lead%20a%20normal%20life.%20Today%2C%20I%20do%20not%20even%20feel%20that%20I%20am%20positive.%20It%20hardly%20matters%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20he%20was%20still%20accepting%20the%20reality%2C%20Gautam%20was%20not%20spared%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F97559%2Fhiv-aids-act-positive-news-legislation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estigma%20and%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20very%20close%20and%20trustworthy%20friend.%20When%20I%20revealed%20my%20status%20to%20him%2C%20he%20was%20empathetic.%20After%20a%20week%2C%20he%20organised%20a%20dinner%20party%20and%20invited%20me.%20But%20before%20I%20reached%20there%2C%20he%20had%20informed%20everyone%20to%20be%20cautious%20as%20I%20was%20HIV%20positive.%20That%20was%20heartbreaking%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recalls%20the%20bullying%20he%20faces%20on%20social%20media.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20use%20dating%20applications%2C%20people%20write%20to%20me%20from%20blank%20profiles%20and%20ask%20why%20I%E2%80%99m%20spreading%20AIDS%2C%20or%20that%20I%20should%20not%20be%20on%20dating%20platforms.%20People%20like%20me%20should%20%E2%80%98die%E2%80%99.%20These%20are%20very%20triggering%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-2-1692620944.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Delhi's%20Gautam%20has%20been%20living%20with%20HIV%20since%20the%20age%20of%2018.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-2-1692620944.jpg%201200w%2C%20h